  "texts": [
    "The dataset of the first cohort was extracted from the Hospital Information System of the Department of Endocrinology and Metabolism at Shanghai Sixth People's Hospital and contained 15,587 patients with diabetes, who underwent annual health checks during a 5-year period.",
    "The second cohort enrolled 3,513 participants with diabetes at baseline from Huadong Sanatorium, and the cohort participants completed 5-year follow-up annually.",
    "Data on demographic information, anthropometric indices, biochemical measurements and retinal images were recorded at baseline and each visit.",
    "The diagnoses of DR grading and DME were based on the macular and optic disc-centered fundus images of each eye at baseline and follow-up visits.",
    "We enrolled eight independent cohorts to serve as external validations."
  ],
